Soft wrap
	-> View port
	-> New line on reaching end of the line
	-> Content will not change

Open file -> Same content wil be displayed

Ask
- Create Library 

Inputs
	- View Port (Number of character / Pixel info)
	- Text that needs to be displayed
	- Constraints

Viewer	
- Zoom-In & Zoom-out? - Not required for library
- Formatting

Output
	- How the content will get displayed
		- Number of characters in each line


String softWrap(String input, int maxChar);

